Package com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.checkreturnvalue

Class ResultUsePolicyEvaluator

java.lang.Object
com.google.errorprone.bugpatterns.checkreturnvalue.ResultUsePolicyEvaluator
public final class ResultUsePolicyEvaluator
extends Object
Evaluates methods and their enclosing classes and packages to determine a ResultUsePolicy for the methods.
